M|Reac|tx|**Version 1.0.0**
M|Reac|tx|Engineering
M|Reac|tx|January 2026
M|Reac|> **|**
M|Reac|tx|> This document is mainly for ag and LLMs to follow when maintaining,
M|Reac|tx|> generating, or refactoring rc codebases using composition. Humans
M|Reac|tx|> may also find it useful, but guidance here is optimized for automation
M|Reac|tx|> and consistency by AI-assisted workflows.
M|Reac|tx|---
M|Abst|tx|Composition patterns for building flexible, maintainable rc cp. Avoid boolean prop proliferation by using compound cp, lifting state, and composing internals. These patterns make codebases easier for both humans and AI ag to work w/ as they scale.
M|Abst|tx|---
M|Tabl|tx|1. [cp Architecture](#1-cp-architecture) — **hi**
